{"tid":846260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"被分手後的我...........","createTime":"2018-10-03T09:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T12:20:02.000Z","uid":209340,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5681100a8449772d85191f9c1c9d198abff437","tid":846260,"uid":209340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"8月頭分被手，一直沉輪係傷心，心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晚晚飲酒，食唔落野，訓唔到教<br />\n一直持續到9月，望到佢已經有新既男朋友<br />\n陪佢過生日，陪佢過中秋。<br />\n我就已經知道我已經係過去式，再不捨都要放下<br />\n<br />\n係分手既時候，做左好多好幼稚既行為<br />\n死纏爛打.........到最後佢block曬我Fb，Ig，Wts，We7，Tg。無辦法去接觸到佢，我個心碎到已經執唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到依家，個人平伏返一半，心依舊會有佢既畫面，但已經挑撥唔到太多情緒岀黎。不過心依舊想佢會解封我，睇我依家既改變，因為佢，教識我點樣去珍惜。由以前自以為是，自私，到依家學會去照顧身邊既人，會企係人地角度諗野，再去決定事情。<br />\n<br />\n時間可以沖淡一切，但又可唔可以沖淡你對我既仇恨？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以由我係你心目中既負數，變返正數？"},{"pid":"42749062c7b6e5610f5703a1ed465cca98757151","tid":846260,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"廢柴"},{"pid":"b5eb3c54839d6a9f5e0efd1ed9030c5d7a7b68b2","tid":846260,"uid":209340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42749062c7b6e5610f5703a1ed465cca98757151","tid":846260,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"廢柴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話曬都初戀啊"},{"pid":"492b5b87547843c335197b8fd3a5578810c48cc2","tid":846260,"uid":1249,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:18:04.000Z","msg":"咁快有新仔，唔荒好女仔"},{"pid":"5cbff0f2b5aaa65d8b4fcd520a0cbf0f2bf759a9","tid":846260,"uid":209340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"492b5b87547843c335197b8fd3a5578810c48cc2","tid":846260,"uid":1249,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:18:04.000Z","msg":"咁快有新仔，唔荒好女仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"有朋友都咁講過。<br />\n但今時今日既社會，我真係好難滲透對與錯。<br />\n佢對我熱既時候，我冷<br />\n到我想去做好既時候，佢走"},{"pid":"ed9744ba65b8a3e588346af7977197f23952c7f2","tid":846260,"uid":194335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"你唔放低都冇用啦 人地都又唔會理你感受"},{"pid":"3464f85a59ec42329a05e0a33cb5e92b888fc286","tid":846260,"uid":209340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed9744ba65b8a3e588346af7977197f23952c7f2","tid":846260,"uid":194335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"你唔放低都冇用啦 人地都又唔會理你感受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:32:01.000Z","msg":"岩啊，所以我選擇放低。<br />\n只係想佢唔好再block我啲野，i still a life"},{"pid":"f2add21a69652a67e147f9269864ab2eedcc291b","tid":846260,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"唔重要了 你亦都唔洗再執著你地之間既連繫<br />\n就當係陌生人就得"},{"pid":"9854e38f2f97901c4e70657a30ed7e0039f995dc","tid":846260,"uid":212348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"你真係廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f0940234fcd243f2e9ad1ba8ed0d6819d902df","tid":846260,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"廢柴<br />\n不過好似見到自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d7fa5956a7310873f2c9a3e59ed3540d700e2e","tid":846260,"uid":209340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2add21a69652a67e147f9269864ab2eedcc291b","tid":846260,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"唔重要了 你亦都唔洗再執著你地之間既連繫<br />\n就當係陌生人就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相識一場，落得呢種結局"},{"pid":"14759e221a8fc05f540a0fb6a8c2f60b45425eb7","tid":846260,"uid":140798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"